dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Trenton, New Jersey, volume 2, sheet 236
dct_description_sm: Includes legend, index key map, "New index, February, 1955" for streets. Includes record of insertion and correction date 1957. "This record supersedes similar record on individual sheets of this map". The updates were paste on the original sheet. "Copyright 1955". These maps were digitized from a copy held by the Trenton Free Public Library, housed in the Trentoniana Collection. Call number: 912.9 INSU
